\phantomsection \addcontentsline{toc}{subsection}{Data and assessment}
The biomass estimate and age composition from the acoustic survey conducted in \Sexpr{survey.end.yr} have been added to the survey time series (Figure~\ref{fig:es-survey-biomass}); earlier survey data (1998--2013) were re-analyzed and updated this year.   % Manual done 2016.
